node.text:
Teaching students how to be an advocate and ally 🏳️‍🌈 can be engaging and creative with this activity! #ad I teamed up with @michaelsstores to help you teach your student about the importance of advocacy.

Be sure to grab all of your favorite multi-colored and alphabet beads for kids at your local Michaels stores for this project with your students! #makeitwithmichaels

#michaelspartner #teachersofig #teachersofinstagram #iteachtoo #teachersofinsta #teachingadvocacy

📣 Hey ELA teachers, we’ve put together a huge bundle of back-to-school resources for you! It’s a combination of our favorite, teacher approved essentials to create a flawless start.

I’ve included my literature review flipbook and my reading literature interactive bulletin board set!

The bundle is 70% off this week only! To check out the different resources included in the pack, tap the link in my bio.

https://thesuperheroteacher.teachable.com/p/back-to-school-bundle-with-secondary-english-coffee-shop

node.text:
Happy 2 year anniversary @m_jeltema10! Words cannot describe how much I adore you.

Thank you for:
♥️ loving me deeply
♥️ caring for me infinitely
♥️ showing me a side of you that so many don’t see. You’re my best friend in every sense.

I want you to know that:
♥️ I will love you and cere for you forever.
♥️ you’re going to be the best mom in the entire world
♥️ you’ve made us the luckiest humans on the planet

Thank you for making my world complete. We love you! 😘

node.text:
A look 👀 inside baby SJ’s nursery! It’s all happening so fast… less than 4 weeks to go!!! Who is ready?!?!?

But really… I need y’all to be ready for me haha.

The nursery is honestly a mixture of a whole bunch of things, but mj reallllllyyyy wanted ocean vibes and I wanted something more boho… so we did our best to fuse the two. Honestly, it looks so much cooler and calming in person! I couldn’t seem to capture it with the 📸.

Today has been a day. TIA for all your support!

#nursery #twomoms #twomomsarebetterthanone #twomomsquad #nurserydecor #lgbtparents #lgbtqfamily

📣 Calling ALL Teachers 📣 Your dream closet awaits 👗! I recently signed up for @teacherstylebox and am super excited to share that they are hosting a giveaway right now to spoil YOU for back-to-school! They're giving ✨5 lucky teachers ✨a free membership of their unlimited clothing rental box for the FULL SCHOOL YEAR!

Click the link in my bio to enter! Giveaway ends TOMORROW, so don’t walk… sprint to my bio!

I love my Teacher Style Box subscription for so many reasons, but here are just a few:
👖 Members get UNLIMITED box swaps all month long (active members can receive and wear two new styles per week - 8/month!)
👖 Shipping is always free both ways!
You can keep anything you love with exclusive discounts up to 90% off retail prices
👖 They carry sizes from XS to 3X
👖 New styles are added to the collection twice a week every Monday and Thursday that fit each season — providing an endless rotation of outfits all year long!

https://bit.ly/TSBgiveaway-BTS-2021

#teacherstylebox #dreamteachercloset #backtoschoolgiveaway #teacherstyleboxgiveaway #freeyearofteacherstyle #iteachtoo #teacherootd #teacherstyle #teacheroutfits #teacherstyleboxpartner

node.text:
✈️🌎 Turn your students into world travelers with this informational text resource! With 20+ nonfiction articles ✏️ and corresponding activities/projects, 📓 your students will learn to dissect and annotate while simultaneously learning about different cultures and countries.

I designed this resource to help students strengthen their reading, writing, and analyzing skills. The journal is designed with 20 unique informational text articles (from 20 countries around the world)! Each article is paired with comprehension questions and a variety of activities and projects.

Link to resource in bio: https://www.teacherspayteachers.com/Product/Travel-Journal-20-Informational-Text-Articles-Activities-Grades-4-7-DIGITAL-4706090

#englishteacher #iteachela #iteachenglish #upperelementary #iteach456 #iteach678 #iteachmiddleschool #informationaltext #iteach5th #iteach6th #middleschoolteacher

node.text:
Do you teach upper elementary, middle school or high school? If so, I have hundreds of teacher approved ✅ activities, projects and bundles to help you prep for back-to-school!

For years, I’ve designed hands-on, engaging resources for you to use with your students. I spend a lot of time on each piece making sure it’s something that it’s appealing AND functional!

In fact, more than 50,000 teachers have given 5-star ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ reviews on my resources.

Today is the last day of the site-wide sale, so be sure to grab anything you need to save!

Link in bio: https://www.teacherspayteachers.com/Store/The-Superhero-Teacher

Ps: this is my Figurative Language Interactive Notebook
